\c 41
\s Jehovha ndiye anorwira vanhu vake
\p
\v 1 Nyararai pamberi pangu, imwi zviwi; uye vanhu ngavavandudze simba; ngavaswedere, zvino vataure; ngatiswedere pamwe chete kumutongo.
\v 2 Ndiani wakamutsa wakarurama kubva kumabvazuva? Akamudanira rutsoka rwake; akapa marudzi pamberi pake; aka\add mu\add*ita atonge \add pamusoro\add* pemadzimambo; aka\add va\add*pa seguruva \add ku\add*munondo wake, sehundi inopepereswa \add ku\add*uta hwake.
\v 3 Akavadzingirira, akapfuura akachengetedzeka nenzira yaasina ku\add mbo\add*famba netsoka dzake.
\v 4 Ndiani wakashanda, aka\add zvi\add*ita, achidana mazera kubva pakutanga? Ini Jehovha, wekutanga newekupedzisira; ndini iye.
\v 5 Zviwi zvakaona zvikatya; migumo yenyika yakadedera, ikaswedera, yakasvika.
\v 6 Vakabatsira umwe neumwe muvakidzani wake, uye kuhama yake anoti: Simba.
\v 7 Zvino muvezi wakasimbisa mupfuri wegoridhe, anorodza nyundo \add wakasimbisa\add* anorova pachipfuriro, achiti pamusoro pekunamatidza: Zvakanaka. Ndokuzvisimbisa nezvipikiri \add kuti\add* zvisazungunuswa.
\p
\v 8 Asi iwe Israeri, muranda wangu, Jakove wandakasarudza, mbeu yaAbhurahama shamwari yangu,
\v 9 iwe wandakatora kubva kumigumo yenyika, ndikakudana kuvakuru vayo, ndikati kwauri: Uri muranda wangu, ndakakusarudza, uye handina kukurasa.
\v 10 Usatya, nokuti ndinewe; usacheuka-cheuka, nokuti ndiri Mwari wako; ndichakusimbisa, zvirokwazvo ndichakubatsira; zvirokwazvo ndichakutsigira neruoko rwerudyi rwekururama kwangu.
\v 11 Tarira, vose vanokutsamwira vachanyadziswa vave nenyadzi; vanorwa newe vachava pasina uye vachaparara.
\v 12 Uchavatsvaka, asi haungavawani; vanhu vanopikisana newe vachava sechinhu pasina; uye vanoita hondo newe vachava sechinhu chisina maturo.
\v 13 Nokuti ini Jehovha, Mwari wako, ndinobata ruoko rwako rwerudyi, ndinoti kwauri: Usatya, ini ndichakubatsira.
\v 14 Usatya iwe Jakove honye, imwi vanhu vekwaIsraeri, ini ndichakubatsirai, anoreva Jehovha, uye mudzikunuri wako, Mutsvene waIsraeri.
\v 15 Tarira, ndakakuita mupuro wakapinza mutsva, une mazino; uchapura makomo, nekuaputsa-putsa, uye uchaita zvikomo zvive sehundi.
\v 16 Uchaarudza, uye mhepo ichaabvisa, nechamupupuri chichaaparadzira; asi iwe uchafara muna Jehovha, uchazvirumbidza muMutsvene waIsraeri.
\p
\v 17 Varombo nevanoshaiwa vanotsvaka mvura, asi haipo; rurimi rwavo rwaoma nenyota. Ini Jehovha ndinovapindura, ini Mwari waIsraeri, handivasii.
\v 18 Ndichazarura nzizi panzvimbo dzakakwirira, nematsime pakati pemipata; renje ndichariita dziva remvura, nenyika yakaoma zvitubu zvemvura.
\v 19 Ndichasima parenje musidhari, muakasia, nemumirite, nemuti wemafuta; ndichaisa mugwenga musipiresi, nemupani, nemufiri pamwe chete;
\v 20 kuti vaone uye vazive uye varangarire nekunzwisisa pamwe chete kuti ruoko rwaJehovha rwaita izvi, uye Mutsvene waIsraeri wakazvisika.
\p
\v 21 Swededzai nyaya yenyu, anoreva Jehovha; swededzai zvinodzivirira zvenyu, anoreva Mambo waJakove.
\v 22 Ngavaswededze, uye vatiudze zvichaitika; ngavataure zvinhu zvekare kuti zvii, kuti ti\add zvi\add*ise mumoyo yedu, tizive mugumo wazvo; kana mutinzwise zvinhu zvinouya.
\v 23 Revai zvinhu zvichauya pashure, kuti tizive kuti muri vamwari; hongu itai zvakanaka kana itai zvakaipa, zvino tichashamiswa titarise \add tose\add* pamwe chete.
\v 24 Tarirai, munobva pasina chinhu, uye basa renyu rinobva pasina, chinyangadzo \add kune\add* anokusarudzai.
\p
\v 25 Ndamutsa \add umwe\add* anobva kumaodzanyemba, zvino wasvika; anobva kumabudazuva, achadana zita rangu; uye achauya \add pamusoro pe\add*machinda sedope, uye semuumbi anokanya ivhu.
\v 26 Ndiani wakareva kubva pakutanga, kuti tizive? Uye kubva panguva yekumashure, kuti titi: Wakarurama? Zvirokwazvo hapana wakareva, zvirokwazvo hapana anonzwisa, zvirokwazvo hapana anonzwa mashoko enyu.
\v 27 Wekutanga \add achati\add* paZiyoni: Tarirai, uvatarire; uye ndichapa kuJerusarema anoparidza mashoko akanaka.
\v 28 Nokuti ndakatarisa, uye kwaiva kusina munhu, uye pakati pavo kusina mupangi wemazano. Zvino ndakavabvunza vakadzosa shoko:
\v 29 Tarirai, vose havana maturo; mabasa avo kushaya maturo; zvifananidzo zvavo zvakaumbwa nekunyungudusa imhepo nekusava nezviripo.
